::GoldenEye::

She looked at the mouse hungrily.  She wanted to swoop down and eat 
loud little mouse.  But then her oppertunity to learn something might 
be lost.  She would wait and bide her time for now.  She looked at 
the ship and wondered if it's scanners had picker her up yet.  Surely 
they have by now, she thought.
